Joan Rivers, Comedienne and Fashion Police Host, Dies at 81

Legendary comedienne Joan Rivers died Thursday after being taken off of life support, her daughter Melissa told The Associated Press. She was 81.

NBC Developing a Johnny Carson Miniseries

Johnny Carson is coming back to NBC. The Peacock is developing a miniseries based on the life of the legendary Tonight Show host, the network announced Thursday.
